verbose_text: Also, there were no statistically significant differences in the ET-1 plasma levels between the patients with RRMS and those with the other progressive courses of MS (PPMS, SPMS, PRMS) : 0.64 +/-0.45 pg/ml (170.85 +/-118.67 fmol/ml) vs. 0.45 +/-0.44 pg/ml (118.77 +/-117.72 fmol/ml) (P = 0.46).
